{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"This article describes the KeyboardKit callout engine.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Callouts are an important part of the typing experience, where input callouts can show the currently pressed key and action callouts can show secondary actions when certain keys are long pressed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit can show an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCallout\/InputCallout","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" for the currently pressed input key, and an "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCallout\/ActionCallout","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" with secondary actions when a key with secondary actions is long pressed."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"👑 ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/KeyboardKit\/KeyboardKitPro","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" unlocks localized callouts for all ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Foundation\/Locale\/keyboardKitSupported","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" locales in your license. Information about Pro features can be found further down.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Namespace","type":"heading","anchor":"Namespace","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit has a "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCallout"},{"type":"text","text":" namespace that contains callout-related types and views. For instance, an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCallout\/InputCallout"},{"type":"text","text":" can show the currently pressed character, and an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCallout\/ActionCallout"},{"type":"text","text":" can show secondary actions."}]},{"text":"Context","type":"heading","anchor":"Context","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit has an observable "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCalloutContext","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class that provides observable input and action callout state, such as the currently pressed "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCalloutContext\/inputAction","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCalloutContext\/secondaryActions","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to present."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"KeyboardKit automatically creates an instance of this class and injects it into ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardInputViewController\/state"},{"text":", then updates this context when keys are pressed.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Services","type":"heading","anchor":"Services","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In KeyboardKit, a "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCalloutService","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can return secondary callout actions when a key is long pressed and trigger feedback when the selected secondary action changes."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"KeyboardKit injects a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCallout\/StandardCalloutService"},{"type":"text","text":" into "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardInputViewController\/services"},{"type":"text","text":". You can replace it at any time, as described further down, or add localized services to it with "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCalloutService\/tryRegisterLocalizedService(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/Keyboard\/Services\/tryRegisterLocalizedCalloutService(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"text":"Styling","type":"heading","anchor":"Styling","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In KeyboardKit, a "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardCallout\/CalloutStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be used to style both input & action callouts. You can apply a custom style with the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/SwiftUICore\/View\/keyboardCalloutStyle(_:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" view modifier, or by returning a custom style with a custom "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.keyboardkit.KeyboardKitPro\/documentation\/KeyboardKitPro\/KeyboardStyleService","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"text":"Views","type":"heading","anchor":"Views","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","t